a man\", \"from\": 563, \"to\": 568}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 582, \"to\": 594}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet an examination of the evidence for such claims made against both boxers shows they appear based almost wholly on a single statement from a Russian official published in the form of a Telegram post last March.\", \"from\": 598, \"to\": 810, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 741, \"end\": 748, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9747129965894091, \"rank\": 0.025942392843968334, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 785, \"end\": 793, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Telegraphy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.118340264809177e-19, \"text\": \"Telegram\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Telegraphy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Telegraphy\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an examination\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 616}, {\"ngram\": \"the evidence\", \"from\": 620, \"to\": 632}, {\"ngram\": \"such claims\", \"from\": 637, \"to\": 648}, {\"ngram\": \"both boxers\", \"from\": 662, \"to\": 673}, {\"ngram\": \"a single statement\", \"from\": 715, \"to\": 733}, {\"ngram\": \"the form\", \"from\": 771, \"to\": 779}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While much of the reporting and commentary has described the two boxers as 'transgender' there is also no evidence or public pronouncements that show either athlete identifies as transgender.\", \"from\": 812, \"to\": 1003, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the reporting\", \"from\": 826, \"to\": 839}, {\"ngram\": \"commentary\", \"from\": 844, \"to\": 854}, {\"ngram\": \"the two boxers\", \"from\": 869, \"to\": 883}, {\"ngram\": \"'transgender\", \"from\": 887, \"to\": 899}, {\"ngram\": \"no evidence\", \"from\": 915, \"to\": 926}, {\"ngram\": \"public pronouncements\", \"from\": 930, \"to\": 951}, {\"ngram\": \"either athlete identifies\", \"from\": 962, \"to\": 987}, {\"ngram\": \"transgender\", \"from\": 991, \"to\": 1002}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They have both competed as women throughout their careers.\", \"from\": 1005, \"to\": 1063, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 1032, \"to\": 1037}, {\"ngram\": \"their careers\", \"from\": 1049, \"to\": 1062}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In recent years, gender eligibility has become a growing controversy in relation to sport and since the most recent Tokyo Olympics some sports bodies have updated their gender rules.\", \"from\": 1065, \"to\": 1247, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"recent years\", \"from\": 1068, \"to\": 1080}, {\"ngram\": \"gender eligibility\", \"from\": 1082, \"to\": 1100}, {\"ngram\": \"a growing controversy\", \"from\": 1112, \"to\": 1133}, {\"ngram\": \"relation\", \"from\": 1137, \"to\": 1145}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 1149, \"to\": 1154}, {\"ngram\": \"the most recent Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1195}, {\"ngram\": \"some sports bodies\", \"from\": 1196, \"to\": 1214}, {\"ngram\": \"their gender rules\", \"from\": 1228, \"to\": 1246}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Several of these governing bodies now ban athletes who went through male puberty from competing in women's events.\", \"from\": 1249, \"to\": 1363, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these governing bodies\", \"from\": 1260, \"to\": 1282}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1299}, {\"ngram\": \"male puberty\", \"from\": 1317, \"to\": 1329}, {\"ngram\": \"women's events\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1362}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, there is also no available evidence to support the idea that either of the boxers at the centre of the controversy went through male puberty.\", \"from\": 1364, \"to\": 1514, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no available evidence\", \"from\": 1387, \"to\": 1408}, {\"ngram\": \"the idea\", \"from\": 1420, \"to\": 1428}, {\"ngram\"