vent, IBA president, Russia's Umar Kremlev posted on his Telegram channel that DNA tests had \\\"proved\\\" both Imane Khelif and Taiwan's Lin Yu-Ting \\\"had XY chromosomes and were thus excluded from the sports events\\\".\", \"from\": 2512, \"to\": 2737, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2531, \"end\": 2534, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.95448574307401, \"rank\": 0.04768458539736475, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}, {\"begin\": 2546, \"end\": 2552, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999699438191283, \"rank\": 2.9835964951894723e-05, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 2555, \"end\": 2559, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Umar\", \"score\": 0.9999999385672728, \"rank\": 6.143256653386171e-08, \"text\": \"Umar\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Umar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Umar\"}, {\"begin\": 2632, \"end\": 2644, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}, {\"begin\": 2649, \"end\": 2655, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"score\": 0.9999995186877889, \"rank\": 4.7563463097683957e-07, \"text\": \"Taiwan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\"}, {\"begin\": 2658, \"end\": 2669, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/L